01:20:25.390 --> 01:20:27.270
with the difficulties
of hydrogen atoms

01:20:27.270 --> 01:20:28.400
in the laboratory.

01:20:28.400 --> 01:20:30.610
We can just use our
favorite alkalize

01:20:30.610 --> 01:20:33.450
and dress the alkalize
up with laser beams

01:20:33.450 --> 01:20:36.280
and eventually create
the same situation

01:20:36.280 --> 01:20:38.770
with an atom which
is experimentally

01:20:38.770 --> 01:20:41.420
much simpler to address.

01:20:41.420 --> 01:20:42.085
Any questions?

